        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository ef5793ad-d069-46e7-9cbf-6fc355ded2bc).Image",
        "Description": "10 years ago, Marco Abiatti&apos;s brother, Mario, was killed in a drunk driving accident. The perpetrators put his body in their car and burried it in the Italian Alps. As it turns out the perps were all friends of Marco Abiatti. The Body was discovered last month and Marco remembers his friends taking a surprise trip up north around the time of his death. Marco still keeps in contact with them and has invited them to his campaign rally. Now it is up to you to take care of them. Good luck.",
